org.azeckoski.reflectutils.map.OrderedMap

Packages that use OrderedMap
org.azeckoski.reflectutils.map A map implementation which supports insertion order retrieval of the keys and values, fully supports removal and interation 
 

Uses of OrderedMap in org.azeckoski.reflectutils.map
 

Classes in org.azeckoski.reflectutils.map that implement OrderedMap
 class ArrayOrderedMap<K,V>
          A map which keeps track of the order the entries are added and allows retrieval of entries in the order they were entered as well, this is NOT safe for multi-threaded access, this is backed by a HashMap and ArrayList
 class ConcurrentOrderedMap<K,V>
          A map which keeps track of the order the entries are added and allows retrieval of entries in the order they were entered as well, this is safe for multi-threaded access, this is backed by a ConcurrentHashMap and Vector
